I was driving to Barnes Station in West London to get a train to Putney Station on early Tuesday Morning to go to Work because I work there every week on the Gateline. On the way driving down there, i was listening to BBC Radio 1 and this track by Daft Punk was playing and it really started my day very well. Normally, I work at Putney Station in the afternoons and evenings but this week, I was covering a collegue of mine who normally does that early morning shift was on holiday for a week so I had the privilege to do that for him/her which was a good thing.

This track is true classic by Daft Punk dating back 22 years ago and it really brings me back to my teenage years in 2001 back then.
